b:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both ModernMT and Weglot share a solid foundation of core features including Machine Translation, Api Access, Real Time. Where ModernMT pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Translation Memory and Custom Models, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. On the other hand, Weglot uniquely offers Glossary and Team Collaboration and Cms Integration, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, ModernMT holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10, while Weglot scores 8/10 overall and 10/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
c:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Weglot comes in at a lower starting price of $15/mo, while ModernMT begins at $25/mo. Neither platform offers a free plan, so you will need to budget for at least the starting tier from the beginning. Be sure to take advantage of any trial periods they may offer."}]]}]
