f:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. ModernMT is best suited for translation agencies, LSPs, high volume translation, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. Weglot, meanwhile, shines for website owners, e commerce, WordPress users, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2017, ModernMT describes itself as \"Adaptive machine translation engine that learns from your corrections in real-time.\" Weglot, established in 2016, positions itself as \"Website translation solution with automatic detection and multilingual SEO.\" Both platforms have been in the market for a similar duration, giving each ample time to refine their offerings and build a loyal user base."}]]}]
10:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Weglot** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to higher user ratings (8.0 vs 7.0), more features (6 vs 5), more competitive pricing. However, this does not mean ModernMT is a poor choice — far from it. ModernMT excels in its own right, particularly for translation agencies and LSPs.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value easiest website translation setup, go with Weglot. If adapts in real-time to your style matters more to you, ModernMT is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
